Anita Gillette https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anita_Gillette 0 Anita Gillette (born August 16, 1936) is an American actress. She is notable for her extensive Broadway credits, her many appearances as a celebrity guest on television game shows, her guest-starring and recurring roles in American television series and for her roles in feature films.
